SEC. 2. The following sitios in the Municipality of Batangas, same province, are constituted as barrios therein, to wit:

Sitio of Pook, barrio Mahabang-Parang, is converted into a barrio, to be known as the barrio of Sorosorong Ilaya, and sitio of Sorosorong Bundoc is converted into a barrio, to be known as the barrio of Sorosorong Ibaba; the boundary line between these barrios shall be a straight running from East to West passing through the center of the barrio school building of Sorosoro;

Sitio of Sorosorong Carzada is converted into a barrio, to be known as the barrio of Sorosorong Carzada;

Sitio Pook ni Mestisa is converted into a barrio, to be known as the barrio of Banabang Silañgan;

Sitio Ilaya is converted into a barrio, to be known as the barrio of Banabang Ilaya;

Sitios Magbabanig, Apple and Ibaba are constituted into a distinct and independent barrio, to be known the barrio of Banabang Ibaba;

Sitios of Kanluran, Silañgang Carzada before Man gahan, Balimbing and Guitnang Pook are constituted into a distinct and independent barrio, to be known as the barrio Banabang Kanluran; and
